ure and the tasks of the War of Resistance Against Japan, to develop the political line of the party, this is: let go and mobilize the masses, expanding the power of the people, under the leadership of the Chinese Communist Party, defeated Japanese invaders, the liberation of the people of the whole country, the establishment of a new democratic doctrine. General Assembly to develop a complete system for the people of the military line. (1 $ dj¦Ó.c¨­m) new party constitution clearly states: the Communist Party of China to unified thinking the theory of Marxism-Leninism with the practice of the Chinese revolution - Mao Zedong Thought, as all work pointer. The General Assembly elected a new Central Committee, Mao Zedong, Zhu De, Liu Shaoqi, Ren Bishi, 44 man-made member of the Central Committee, Liao Chengzhi, Wang Jiaxiang 33 alternate member. <br>'
